=== Social Media Pack - Twitter Module ===
Contributors: Matt Porter, Nick Rogers
Donate Link: http://www.socialmediapack.co.uk/wordpress/social-media-pack-twitter-plugin-with-oauth/
Tags: twitter, social networking
Requires at least: 2.0
Tested up to: 3.0.1
Stable tag: 1.2

This module forms a part of the Social Media Pack, the Twitter module cross posts to a nominated Twitter account using the oauth method. It is very simple to install and use.


== Description ==

This is a relatively small script which allows you to automatically send your
blog posts to twitter and keep any people that may be following you updated with
your latest activity. The module uses oauth to connect to Twitter and is.gd to compress back links.

== Installation ==

1. Upload socialmediapack.zip
2. Activate the plugin
3. Go to the "Settings" menu and select "SMP - Twitter", follow the instructions
   to authorize and link your twitter account with your wordpress site

